{"tid":664490,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國際特赦組織通訊軟體隱私排名：Facebook 第","createTime":"2018-05-14T06:18:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T06:24:35.000Z","uid":186201,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e65c242d7c968460b05626d5e24ad421c7d91dca","tid":664490,"uid":186201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T06:18:51.000Z","msg":"國際特赦組織通訊軟體隱私排名：Facebook 第一，QQ、WeChat 零分<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://technews.tw/2016/10/25/amnesty-international-which-messaging-app-is-best-for-protecting-privacy/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2016%2F10%2F25%2Famnesty-international-which-messaging-app-is-best-for-protecting-privacy%2F&d=fq0aq0RQIHg2u0X0ok2fbi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=508faa96\" target=\"_blank\">http://technews.tw/2016/10/25/amnesty-international-which-messaging-app-is-best-for-protecting-privacy/</a><br />\n<br />\n現今社會重視個人隱私，不少人選用手機通訊軟體時除了著重功能，也會關注軟體在隱私保密、通訊安全上的表現。國際特赦組織針對 11 間科技公司旗下的即時通訊軟體做通訊保密評估，日前公布評分結果：Facebook 旗下的 FB Messenger 和 WhatsApp 隱私度最高，得到 73 分；騰訊旗下的 QQ 和 WeChat 則以 0 分「吊車尾」"},{"pid":"88cf63f9c5c1942093f73a91f7fbebb1db8683a1","tid":664490,"uid":186201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T06:21:08.000Z","msg":"我知我old news<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最近諗過用交友app/wechat<br />\n擔心用wechat 有back door<br />\n見到哩篇新聞<br />\n諗緊今時今日 排位又有咩唔同<br />\n或者係 仲有咩係值得用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac093b7e368c780c7498877becd7a3349de4f669","tid":664490,"uid":35014,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T06:21:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4187996b15ff3c6616a09c2c19f868cc17c32175","tid":664490,"uid":91685,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T06:23:10.000Z","msg":"FB同獲濕最高分? 收左豬西幾多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86331dc04b8d67fab5455e9fd215f9f3e31fc86c","tid":664490,